formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This certificate is issued for QE Purpose only. Incurred and Paid details are taken as per the tally backup made available up to December 31,2018. We do not certify the Areas mentioned in the certificate and the KYC mentioned in the certificate. All the sale deed for the projects executed by the promoter however the details pertaining to the same is not made available to us. Promoter has not opened RERA Bank Account this project was registered in RERA But BU permission was received immediately after registration and only QE requirement was only to be filed. The details pertaining to RERA bank
account is basically the current account operated by the promoter for this project. We have taken opening balance from 24-7-2017 the date of opening of RERA Account. The Withdrawal is considered as whatever cost in incurred & paid. We have not taken any estimation pertaining to onsite exp or fees or interest etc as the same has not been provided to us by the management.
